spaceteam for 3 people but you have to play it with 1 person

you are a galactic mail carrier and the mail service is broke and understaffed
you have to deliver mail
space messenger pigeons

consoles
    helm
    navigation
    shields
    engineering
    airlock
    manual/documentation

modal interface:
    you can't see any of the other screens in any mode

    walking around your ship : you can see where you are in the ship interior

    helm : you can see your surroundings

    nav console : you can see where you are
        gives you an arrow, that's it
        view your destination goal
        press a button and it slowly expands from your point

    shields console : look at your health
        your health bar
        you can turn on a protective shield, but you have to hold a button the whole time
        panic "kill engine" button, stops you motionless in space

    engineering console : repairing systems
        shields-on button
            

    airlock console : push the letter out the airlock once you're at your destination
       you have to get close to the planet without crashing
       shove the letter out the spaceship towards the planet

    manual/documentation console : read the instructions for the game
        outdated, bad docs
        how the player learns

simple random generation, infinite scrolling space in any direction
    fixed 2d space generated on startup
        every time you get to an objective, regenerate the entire space

ontrols:
    interior:
        you hold the mouse and your character walks toward that
    consoles:
        

obstacles and the 2 or more consoles you have to juggle
    static and moving asteroids
        helm
        shields/status
            repair

        they shake your screen and make a muted thunk
            if it's smaller than X, it makes screen shake and thunk but no health loss

    pirates: asteroids that shoot at you

    if you go outside the space you are penalized

    asteroid dust fields
        you have to keep the shields button pressed while passing through or else you lose health

space physics
    no friction
